column108: Valsøytunet, Valsøyfjord, Norway, is looking for a chef. Job description working in the kitchen Skills you nead to have education as a chef, and some experience Contract temporary contract about 15.05.2025 - 15.10.2025, ca. 8 hours per day Salary about NOK 250 per hour We can help with accomodation. More information jobb@valsoya.no How to apply? send your application to jobb@valsoya.no Latest application day is 15.03.2025 (from NAV EURES Norway) At Valsøytunet, we offer accommodation,camping and good dining experiences to our guests throughout the summer. We are a small holiday destination for families, and we have an associated climbing park within walking distance of us. Valsøytunet started in 1996 as a campsite and has since moved many houses to Valsøya which have been renovated and put into use as accommodation units and a restaurant. We have simply started with the reuse of houses.  Since 1996, Valsøytunet has grown to become hotel-like business with 14 unique accommodation units, almost 50 drop-in campsites and a restaurant with space for a total of 130 dining guests.  https://www.valsoya.no
